<asp:Content ID="Content2" ContentPlaceHolderID="ContentPlaceHolder1" Runat="Server">

    <section style="padding: 70px 0;">
    <div class="auto-container" style="max-width:1100px; margin:auto; color:#333;">
        
        <h1 style="font-size:42px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:20px; color:#222;">
            Privacy Policy – MobileNest 📱✨
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size:16px; line-height:1.8;">
            Welcome to <strong>MobileNest</strong>. We respect your privacy like it’s our own. 
            Hum aapke personal data ko safe rakhne ke liye committed hain — no cap. 
            Yaha hum explain kar rahe hain ke hum kya collect karte hain, kaise handle karte hain, 
            aur kis situation me share karte hain. Aap hamare users ho — hamari respect ho.
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">1️⃣ What Data We Collect</h2>
        <p style="line-height:1.8;">
            - Name, Email, Phone number (jaise aap account banate waqt dete ho)<br />
            - Delivery Address & Order Details<br />
            - Device info, IP Address, cookies — website improving ke liye<br />
            - Customer service interactions (calls, chats, emails)
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">2️⃣ How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p style="line-height:1.8;">
            - Aapko products deliver karne ke liye ✅<br />
            - Aapko order & delivery updates dene ke liye 📦<br />
            - Scam se protection & security updates ke liye 🔐<br />
            - Offers & updates (sirf jab aap allow karo) 🎧<br />
            - Website experience ko next-level banane ke liye ⚡
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">3️⃣ We Protect Your Data</h2>
        <p style="line-height:1.8;">
            Hum advanced security protocols use karte hain — anti-fraud walls, encrypted storage, 
            SSL protection, so your data stays locked tight. 🛡  
            Hum kabhi bhi aapka data kisi third-party ko <strong>sell</strong> nahi karte. NEVER.
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">4️⃣ Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p style="line-height:1.8;">
            Hum data sirf un companies ke saath share karte hain jo delivery & website support me help karti hain:
            courier partners, payment gateways, trusted service providers.  
            Bas — no bakwaas sharing.
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">5️⃣ Cookies 🍪</h2>
        <p style="line-height:1.8;">
            Cookies se hum aapke shopping experience ko improve karte hain — recommendations, 
            cart memory, smooth browsing. Agar chahe to browser me cookies block kar sakte ho.
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">6️⃣ Your Rights (Boss Mode)</h2>
        <p style="line-height:1.8;">
            Aap hamesha chaho toh:  
            ✔ Apna data access kar sakte ho  
            ✔ Correction karva sakte ho  
            ✔ Data delete karva sakte ho  
            ✔ Marketing mails se OUT ho sakte ho  
            Ek request drop karo — we got you.
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">7️⃣ Policy Updates</h2>
        <p style="line-height:1.8;">
            Technology evolve hoti rehti hai. Hum bhi.  
            Agar policy me changes honge, yahi update kar diya jayega. Stay tuned. 👀
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">8️⃣ Contact Us Anytime</h2>
        <p style="line-height:1.8;">
            Kisi bhi query, concern ya chai-pe-charcha type support ke liye —  
            <strong>Team MobileNest 💛</strong> hamesha available.  
            Email: cybervishu055@gmail.com  
            Phone: +91 98765 43210
        </p>

        <div style="margin-top:50px; padding:20px; border-left:4px solid #ff7a00; background:#fff;">
            <strong>We exist because you trust us.</strong><br/>
            And trust… we guard like treasure. 🔒✨
        </div>

    </div>
</section>


